    "body" : "<pre><code> //Inside main class  \n\n int resID = getId(buttonID);\n\n findViewById(resID);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Use the method below</p>\n<pre><code> private int getId (String resourceName) {\n   \n try {\n\n        Field idField = R.id.class.getDeclaredField(resourceName);\n\n        return idField.getInt(idField);\n\n    } catch (Exception e) {\n\n        throw new RuntimeException(&quot;No resource ID found for: &quot;\n                + resourceName + &quot; / &quot;, e);\n\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>For ID use R.id.class</p>\n<p>For Drawable Use R.Drawable.class</p>\n"
